<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style></style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div
      style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f5f5f5; color: #475467; max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; background-image: url('https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mosip/documentation/1.2.0/docs/_images/header_background.png'); border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 20px; padding: 0 2px 1rem 2px;"
      cellpadding="0"
      cellspacing="0"
      width="600"
    >
      <div style="color: #ffffff; text-align: left; padding: 24px 36px;">
        <img
          style="height: 58px; width: 150px; vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 10px;"
          src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mosip/documentation/1.2.0/docs/_images/new_Mosip_logo.png"
          alt="Logo"
        />
      </div>
      <div style="padding: 20px 36px; line-height: 1.5; background-color: #ffffff;">
        <div style="font-size: 14px;">
          <p><strong>Dear ${partnerId},</strong></p>
          <p>
            This is to inform you that the API Key named <strong>${apiKeyName}</strong> associated with policy:
            <strong>${policyName}</strong> is scheduled to expire on <strong>${expiryDateTime} UTC</strong>.
            To ensure continued functionality and uninterrupted services, we request you to upload the certificate for renewal before the expiration date.
          </p>
          <div style="padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #FAFBFC; border-radius: 10px;">
            <p style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">API Key Details</p>
            <hr style="border-top: 1px solid #E5E5E5;" />
            <p style="padding: 5px 0px; font-weight: 600;">
              API Key Name<br /><span style="font-weight: 400;">${apiKeyName}</span>
            </p>
            <p style="padding: 5px 0px; font-weight: 600;">
              Partner Domain<br /><span style="font-weight: 400;">AUTH</span>
            </p>
            <p style="padding: 5px 0px; font-weight: 600;">
              Expiration Date & Time<br /><span style="font-weight: 400;">${expiryDateTime} UTC</span>
            </p>
            <p style="padding: 5px 0px; font-weight: 600;">
              Policy Group<br /><span style="font-weight: 400;">${policyGroup}</span>
            </p>
            <p style="padding: 5px 0px; font-weight: 600;">
              Policy Name<br /><span style="font-weight: 400;">${policyName}</span>
            </p>
            <p style="padding: 5px 0px; font-weight: 600;">
              Action Required<br />
              <span style="font-weight: 400;">Generate a new API Key in ‘Authentication Services’.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          <p>
            Failure to renew the API Key before its expiration may result in service disruptions.
          </p>
          <p>To proceed with the API Key generation, please follow these steps:</p>
          <ol>
            <li>Log in to your account on the PMS Portal.</li>
            <li>Navigate to ‘Authentication Services’ under the Partner Dashboard.</li>
            <li>Click on ‘Generate API Key’ button within the API Key tab.</li>
            <li>Fill the API Key details and submit.</li>
            <li>The API Key is generated — please copy and store it securely as it will not be displayed again.</li>
          </ol>
          <p>
            Please note that the expiry date and time are provided in UTC format, so kindly account for any time zone differences when planning your renewal.
          </p>
          <p>Thank you for your prompt attention to this matter.</p>
          <p>Best regards,<br />MOSIP</p>
          <p style="padding: 6px 0px;">
            ** This is an auto-generated email. Please do not reply to this email. **
          </p>
          <p>
            Website:
            <a target="_blank" href="https://www.mosip.io">www.mosip.io</a>
          </p>
          <hr style="border-top: 1px solid #edeef0;" />
        </div>
        <div style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <div style="margin: auto; border-collapse: collapse; text-align: center;">
            <a
              target="_blank"
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/mosip-project/posts/?feedView=all"
            >
              <img
                src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mosip/documentation/1.2.0/docs/_images/linkedin.png"
                alt="linkedin"
                style="width: 24px; height: 24px; padding: 0px 4px;"
              />
            </a>
            <a target="_blank" href="https://www.youtube.com/@mosip16">
              <img
                src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mosip/documentation/1.2.0/docs/_images/youtube.png"
                alt="youtube"
                style="width: 24px; height: 24px; padding: 0px 4px;"
              />
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
